name: Xeno Tezors #02 - Princess Amira
description: Princess and future queen of planet Trealla. Her people had to suffer many years during a huge infestation of the lichworms. Shaped by this experience her plan for Trealla is to resign from the intergalactic association and ban all outgoing and incoming spaceflights to avoid a new spread of the lichworms which often come unrecognized in deliveries from other planets. The idea to become a species living for themselves on only one planet like in ancient times is finding many followers.
